+ Dung flex de lam gi?
	+ dan trang
	+ Dan trang flex => chua an toan
	+ Float, clear

+ Float, clear => nho nho, it quan trong => flex

+ Float:
	+ Tat ca cac element deu troi len phia tren, ben trai
	+ Float: element se troi sang ben trai hoac phai
	+ Nen: 1 cai float trai, 1 cai float sang phai	

+ Van de cua float:
	+ Khi float mot thanh phan => thang cha => ko tinh toan duoc chieu cao

+ Chia 3 cot:
	+ float left het

+ Clear:
	+ Chan khong cho cac thanh phan ben duoi troi len phan thua
	+ both: ca hai (ca ben trai va ben phai)
	+ left: clear ben trai
	+ right: clear ben phai

+ Neu phia truoc co thanh phan dang float => clear di => nam rieng 1 dong => clear both: 

+ Clearfix:
+ pseudo element:

+ Text va cac thuoc tinh cua text:
+ Chu: hinh anh => lay tu font
+ Dong chu: la cac hinh chu nhat duoc sap xep lien nhau theo chieu doc
+ Chu cai => xep nam giua dong chu theo chieu doc
+ line-height: do cao dong: chieu cao cua dong chu
+ font-size: do cao cua chu cai
+ letter-spacing: khoang cach giua 2 chu cai
+ word-spacing: khoang cach giua 2 tu (dau cach)
+ text-transform: uppercase - lowercase
+ text-indent: can le
	+ text-indent: -1000000px;
+ text-align: can le chu (left/right/center)

=> de can giua chu trong mot element:
	Dat height = line-height => hien thi chinh xac 1 dong chu